Marsh & McLennan Cos., the second-
biggest insurance broker, named Julio A. Portalatin president
and chief executive officer of its Mercer human-resources
consulting unit.  Portalatin joins the broker from American International
Group Inc., the bailed-out insurer, where he was president and
CEO of growth economies at property-casualty unit Chartis,
according to a statement today from New York-based Marsh &
McLennan.  To contact the reporter on this story:
